metadata.name: 0: THE FOOL
metadata.description:
"The very first arcana of all. The Fool is not the card of foolish, but about a traveler who have a brave heart. It's a symbol of a new beginning. 

Tell like a tales about the young red haired girl who's brave enough to travel through an unknown night, where even darkness will never makes her heart crumble, as beyond the night sky there's always a stars lighten up the whole night sky, and with the ground full of fireflies to lighten up the sacred field. 

In every journey there's always a light to guide your way."
